name: Early Ludwig
description: This is the “First collection of the life and times of Ludwig the Undead”. A series of 500 NFTs featuring 100 unique hand made artworks by Vee, the Beethoven X designer. This collection was minted to the 500 early liquidity providers and closest supporters of the Beethoven X project. The artworks were inspired by music, culture and current events happening on this fast moving planet. Enjoy the show.
